Pagination helps in returning limited amount of data per second, improving performance, reducing db load. Example: transaction history, social media reels
Offset Pagination and Cursor based pagination.
Cursor=encoded last seen record
Auto incremental ids are used as cursor. On each request cursor is store and pass into new subsequent request. (Example: (created_at,id) for transaction history)

